	- [doc] Mention Text::Table::HTML::DataTables.


0.004   2021-03-11  Released-By: PERLANCAR; Urgency: medium

	- Allow cell to be hashref containing keys like 'text', 'colspan'
	  (optional), and 'rowspan' (optional), just like in
	  Text::Table::More.


